title: Ranked games BEFORE shutdown
body: i won a game without any Laggers or dcs but when i came out it doesnt even have my game in history or LP gains just wondering if this is temp or we dont get W for last game

replies.body: same thing happened to me and when i tried to start a new normal game, it said i was already ingame so I relogged and now it comes up witht he reconnect button that doesn't even work. Rito plz
Just wait it out, it has happened before. It will be fixed soon and you will be able to reconnect.

It is announced that ranked queues were down due to an issue. Perhaps the game and lp is not showing due to ranked being down. Once it is back up you will find out and most likely the game will show. 

"We've temporarily disabled the RANKED_QUEUE queues while we investigate an issue that's negatively impacting games."
